{
  "stem": "2460.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I looked out from the window, it didn't mean too much to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because nobody, I think nobody, knew what is Auschwitzen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a tiny little town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I saw the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody saw that we are in Auschwitzen, the train station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the train slowed down, slowly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then it passed the train station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the train was traveling another 10 minutes probably, or 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very, very slow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the-- the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was afternoon, late afternoon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And all of a sudden, it-- the train stopped, and it was very quiet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And all of a sudden, all the doors from the entire convoy, I think there were 40 or 42, or even more.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The train was very, very long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The doors, those heavy wooden doors, at once, they opened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the yellings from these strange-looking people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They jumped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The different language-- [GERMAN], out!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- the-- everything sounded like you-- you are in a madhouse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Everything was so-- so unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Fast, fast.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Out.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Out.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[GERMAN], from the-- from the boxcars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we were jumping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were trying to help the older people to get off from the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they pushed us away, those strange-dressed people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That they were prisoners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Polish prisoners, that they were, already, many years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wore the blue and gray-striped dress with this round hat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they looked terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know that they are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they looked like animals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They behaved like animals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were just ordering us, very quick, to leave the-- the boxcars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were trying to catch our belongings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, you don't need it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
